UniCredit Managing Sale of 2.73 Million IMA Shares

-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i   a n d   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-03-22T15:35:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/unicredit-equita-managing-sale-of-2-73-million-ima-shares-1-.html
(Corrects story originally published March 21 to show
Equita SIM is co-lead manager.)  UniCredit Spa (UCG)  is managing the sale
of 2.73 million IMA SpA shares, according to a statement from
the Italian maker of packaging machines.  UniCredit is sole global coordinator for the deal and
Equita SIM SpA is co-lead manager.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francesca Cinelli in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  